SINGER: ♪ Come a little closer♪

28:59.259 --> 29:01.130
[chuckles]

29:01.174 --> 29:02.958
SINGER: ♪ So I can see
your sweat drip ♪

29:03.002 --> 29:04.264
[laughs]

29:04.307 --> 29:07.571
♪ I'll make you my soldier♪

29:07.615 --> 29:09.269
♪ You're gonna have
