-Yes!
-Wow, wow, wow, wow, wow.

37:15.972 --> 37:17.844
-Amazing.
-Wow.

37:17.887 --> 37:19.541
-That was beautiful, Raelle.
-Thank you.

37:19.585 --> 37:20.629
Mm-hmm.

37:28.028 --> 37:30.160
-All quiet?
-Yeah. It's a ghost town.

37:30.204 --> 37:31.727
It'll pick up next week.
Once the troops start

37:31.771 --> 37:33.773
rolling back in.

37:33.816 --> 37:34.991
[exhales sharply]

37:40.475 --> 37:42.651
South Gate, report!

37:44.610 --> 37:49.049
[vocalizing]

37:50.833 --> 37:54.576
[pounding on door]

38:14.509 --> 38:18.557
[sinister music playing]

38:41.710 --> 38:43.016
Hi.

38:45.801 --> 38:47.325
Oh, my.

38:48.848 --> 38:51.720
[breathing heavily]

38:53.635 --> 38:55.681
[grunts]

38:55.724 --> 38:57.378
Oh, deal with her.

38:57.422 --> 38:59.467
[groaning]

39:01.730 --> 39:03.384
[grunting]

39:42.118 --> 39:44.599
Oh, I can't wait
for Silver to see this.

39:59.005 --> 40:00.093
Pity.

40:01.442 --> 40:04.924
I would have loved
to talk to you about your work.

40:04.967 --> 40:08.231
You were, apparently,
quite extraordinary.

40:10.973 --> 40:14.020
[shushing]

40:36.608 --> 40:41.003
WOMAN:
♪ I'll be your mirror ♪

40:41.047 --> 40:42.701
♪ I'll be your mirror ♪

40:42.744 --> 40:45.443
Hello. Mother.

40:52.145 --> 40:53.886
What's happening?

40:53.929 --> 40:54.930
Whatever it is, we need to go.

40:54.974 --> 40:56.062
Wait...

40:56.105 --> 41:00.240
[indistinct whispering]

41:00.283 --> 41:01.981
Fort Salem has fallen.

41:02.024 --> 41:05.114
-What?
-Fort Salem has fallen.

41:05.158 --> 41:06.681
I can't make it out.

41:06.725 --> 41:08.161
It's just garbled
and chaotic, and...

41:08.204 --> 41:09.989
What?

41:10.032 --> 41:11.686
ANACOSTIA: Just--if you would
just give me a moment

41:11.730 --> 41:13.383
-to try to listen.
-STERLING: What are they saying?

41:13.427 --> 41:15.995
-ANACOSTIA: It's just frantic.
-STERLING: We gotta move.

41:16.038 --> 41:18.214
-We gotta get going.
-Rae.

41:20.260 --> 41:22.567
No.

41:22.610 --> 41:24.612
[inhales sharply]
They're back.

41:34.013 --> 41:36.058
SINGER: ♪ I'll be your mirror ♪

41:36.102 --> 41:38.452
♪ Reflect what you are♪

41:38.496 --> 41:40.367
♪ In case you don't know♪

41:40.410 --> 41:42.978
♪ I'll be the wind♪

41:43.022 --> 41:45.372
♪ The rain and the sunset ♪

41:45.415 --> 41:47.853
♪ The light on your door♪

41:47.896 --> 41:50.464
♪ To show that you're home♪

41:50.508 --> 41:54.860
♪ Please put down your hands♪

41:54.903 --> 41:58.603
♪ 'Cause I see you♪

41:58.646 --> 42:02.607
♪ I'll be your mirror ♪
